	 Mobile barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venue reserves the r
	ight to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each person must
	 have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is no elevator.
	 Stairs and ramps only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag search
	 at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When 
	purchasing ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by emai
	l if assistance is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you m
	ay reach us at accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses 
	an armless freestanding chair for patrons with mobility impairments and th
	eir companions. Please note that our historic theatre has no elevator to t
	he balcony levels.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/amplify-courage-a-conce
	rt-for-school-seattle-washington-04-04-2026/event/0F006461C897B2A4\n\nFrom
